# ACCOUNT ==============================================

### GET ALL ACCOUNTS OF CURRENT USER
GET {{BASE_URL}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}


### GET ACCOUNT BY ID
GET {{BASE_URL}}/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}

### POST ACCOUNT
POST {{BASE_URL}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{JWT_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

